description: When Dr. Ramzi is called to the UAE to psychoanalyze a recent kidnap-victim, he learns that this traumatized young woman is actually Noora the Light, the second of THE 99! But how did Noora escape her kidnappers on her own, and what is the dark secret she is holding in?

Jami the Assembler can build anything with the power of his Noor Stone, but he's a kid who's spent most of his life in a lab, with no one but machines and scientists for company. When he meets THE 99, his power goes haywire! Jami the Assembler is out of control-- can THE 99 help him use his gem for good?

Jabbar the Powerful is in the arena fight of his life against champion Mumita the Destroyer, whose Noor Stone-powered gauntlet makes her nearly indestructible. Will Mumita the Destroyer destroy Jabbar? Or will she hear his pleas to change her vicious ways?
